n responsible for business sales and product growth on a global scale drawing on his extensive international experience to manage european and asian sales teams all while spearheading the company’s marketing initiatives and service delivery teams    location of member   upcoming events you have not posted any events at this time what you see below is just a sample this coming sunday feb   pm to  pm feb   midwood avenue beverly hills ca  view details next sunday feb   pm to  pm feb   parkway drive beverly hills ca  view details professional information title  commercial director marketing area  international type of business  maritime products  services business website  wwwaxsmarinecom industry  business management company name  axs marine expertise  responsible for managing vertical business sales and lateral product growth on a global basis managing european and asian sales teams direct company marketing plans and service delivery teams years of experience in industry   years personal information gender  male linkedin profile  wwwlinkedincominstephenjfletcher education degrees   years of experience favorite business publication  economist financial times hobbiessports  enjoys spending time with family and playing golf professional biography products andor services  provides a complete set of interactive internet based decisionmaking tools and databases which support all commercial ship chartering activities formed in june  and has over  clients for its  specialized product lines axs dry alphaliner axss  p and axs tanker the products and solutions are purposely built for ship brokers operators owners characters research firms and financial institutions using state of the art internet technologies   affiliations awards  british chamber of commerce in singapore   more about me  stephen is the commercial director for axs marine a company producing a comprehensive set of interactive database and decision making tools for all types of clients in the marine industry laun